  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h1>Adds</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Allow the user to dismiss Backup restore card until a new restore is made</li>\n<li>Add tooltip with more info when there's a deploy timeout activity</li>\n<li>Add \"Go To Services Page\" link on Overview page</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Changes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>When downloading logs, the timestamp will be based on the local timezone</li>\n<li>Update Status page links pointing to the right environments (us-west-1, eu-west-1)</li>\n<li>Improve description of Reset Password page and email</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Fixes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixes several inconsistencies with \"skip\" flags on custom domains</li>\n<li>Fix certification removal even if it was skipped</li>\n<li>Fix a DNS problem when updating custom domains</li>\n<li>Fix styles on \"Mark as read\" buttons</li>\n</ul>"
      },
